BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260314T104800
DTEND:20260314T140000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.911ft at 10:48\n-0.005ft at 14:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Old\, mid-period S swell has well exposed spots in waist to shoulder surf 
 in the morning\, as best breaks still see overhead sets\, after the dawn p
 atrol high tide backs out a bit. Secondary NW swell lingers. Waves dip dur
 ing the day. \n\nLight southerly breeze\, clean to semi-clean conditions t
 hrough the day. 
END:VEVENT
