BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260315T113000
DTEND:20260315T141800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.928ft at 11:30\n-0.052ft at 14:18\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Modest scale combo of old and new S-SSW swell\, plus lingering NW swell\, 
 for mainly thigh to stomach high waves\, chest sets at top breaks. High ti
 de slows down most spots during the first half of the morning\, then ebbin
 g tide helps through mid day. \n\nLight/variable to light southerly winds 
 due through the day for nice conditions. 
END:VEVENT
