BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260316T121200
DTEND:20260316T145400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.888ft at 12:12\n-0.022ft at 14:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Fresh round of long-period SSW Southern Hemi on the rise\, while secondary
  NW swell persists. Better summertime spots are running chest to head high
 \, while focal points see overhead sets\, showing most consistently over t
 he afternoon. Mid morning high tide slows down tide sensitive spots. \n\nC
 onditions looking clean all day with light\, primarily offshore winds. 
END:VEVENT
