BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260317T124800
DTEND:20260317T154200
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.949ft at 12:48\n-0.003ft at 15:42\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Long-period\, steep-angled SSW Southern Hemi tops out\, as some secondary 
 mid-period WNW swell joins in. That swell blend puts lots of spots in wais
 t to shoulder high waves\, as best summertime exposures and standout combo
  breaks hit a foot+ overhead. Mid morning high tide will bog down tide sen
 sitive spots. \n\nLight winds due all day\, offshore for the morning\, gen
 tle sea breeze in the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
